Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Agusta 2020
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna daidaito tsakanin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / EU da Kasashen Kasuwancin Kasuwanci da Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa annobar COVID-19 tana cikin matakai daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk duniya.
Bisa ga abin da ya faru a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da dakunan kulawa da gaggawa suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don karuwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman masu kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na 2019, an gano wasu marasa lafiya da cutar huhu a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga kwayar cutar coronavirus da ba a san asalinta ba wanda yanzu aka sani da cutar sankarar numfashi mai tsanani coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Binciken ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da cutar nimoniya ko babu, kuma mafi yawan lokuta suna warkewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kwantar da hankali a asibiti kuma kashi 6% na mutane suna da mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke mutuwa a asibiti ya kai kusan kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika ƙaruwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Turai (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu yankuna kuma halin COVID-19 ya sake farfadowa a wasu sassan duniya bayan wannan.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris na 2020, Babban Sakataren Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an gano mutum na farko a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 lokacin da aka dawo da shi daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga watan Agusta, 2020, an gano cutar COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, wanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da ranar da aka haɗa, akwai mutane 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 yayin da suke ƙaruwa
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta ƙididdigar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, daga shafukan yanar gizo na hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Duniya, cibiyoyin lafiya na WHO da wuraren tafiye-tafiye, kowace rana da karfe 2:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don nazarin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, tare da kwatanta shi da na Italiya.
A matsayin hanyar ƙididdige yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke cikin magani, mun ƙididdige yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da aka rarraba cikin kwanaki 14, a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da UK, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa kamar yadda ya karu a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 2:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris.
Halin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya sun yi daidai da na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto na 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, adadin sabbin cututtukan COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Source).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda karuwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun sami karuwar masu kamuwa da COVID-19 (Tushen).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Agusta da karfe 2:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK 15 suna da adadin adadin masu cutar da suka yi daidai da Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Yanayin da aka samu a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana nuna cewa cutar tana ƙaruwa a cikin ƙasa ɗaya.
Wannan ya kasance haka har ma da ƙasashe da ke da matakan kiwon lafiya daban-daban, da ma'auni daban-daban don tantancewa da kuma ƙididdigar ƙididdigar mutane don gwajin COVID-19, gami da ƙara yawan gwajin.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana cewa kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma rahotanni sun nuna cewa asibitoci da dakunan kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun cika.
Adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibiti da / ko dakunan kulawa na gaggawa a cikin EU / EEA ya kai kashi 6% da 1% daidai da haka, (ba a nuna waɗannan bayanan ba).
Maimakon haka, ya kamata a tattara su cikin tsari mai kyau bisa ga bayanan da aka bayar game da yawan masu cutar da kuma mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin wuraren kula da marasa lafiya da kuma wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, inda a Jamus akwai gadaje 29.2 da kuma Portugal akwai gadaje 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa akwai wasu ƙasashe da ke da ƙarin ko ƙasa da Italiya (gadoji 12.5 na asibiti mai tsanani da na alurar riga kafi ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 201011).
Abubuwan da ke tattare da wadatar kayan aikin kiwon lafiya, dangane da kwatancen yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da UK da kuma yiwuwar buƙatar gado mai mahimmanci ya wuce kashi 90%, an bayyana a cikin rahoton ECDC na shida na saurin haɗarin haɗari kan COVID-19.
Saboda har yanzu akwai wasu yankuna a cikin EU / EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da dakunan jinya na gaggawa suna ba da sabis ga mutane a cikin yankuna da aka sani, za a sami bayanan marasa lafiya da gadajen jinya ta hanyar Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Abubuwan da ke faruwa a Italiya da sauran ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, asibitoci da dakunan kulawa na gaggawa suna buƙatar shirya don yanayin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 tsakanin al'ummomin da kuma karuwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda yake a yankunan da ke cikin Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin nazarin gaggawa na ECDC, shirye-shirye na gaggawa yana da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, gami da sauyawa daga hana yaduwa zuwa warkarwa, saboda saurin karuwar yawan masu cutar da ake tsammani a cikin hukumomi ba zai ba hukumomi da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don ganewa, yarda da aiwatar da matakan da suka dace ba idan ba a aiwatar da su ba.
Binciken farko na cutar ya nuna hanyoyin kiwon lafiya don magance matsalar.
Akwai ɗan takaddama game da yadda ƙasashe za su iya haɓaka ƙarfin su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan ya gaza, ana sa ran cewa za a matsa wa tsarin kiwon lafiya a sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA saboda yawan marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da mummunan cututtukan numfashi (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta sami sama da 80,000 a China da sauran ƙasashe, wanda ya haifar da bala'in jama'a.
Kamar dai yadda yake tare da SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai saurin kamuwa da cutar kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba shi da ƙarfi kamar SARS kuma yana kashe mutane kaɗan amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
Dangane da yawan wallafe-wallafen da aka buga game da cutar, wannan shafin yana nufin gabatar da cikakken nazarin binciken da aka yi game da cutar.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da cututtuka, abin da ke jawo su, ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, da kuma yadda za a yi tsinkaya da kuma guje wa su.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna da tabbacin cewa wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma magance wannan cuta mai tsanani.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga Sinawa da aka umarce su da su zauna a gidajen su a duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni masu zuwa saboda barkewar cutar da ba a sani ba.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da mummunan ciwon numfashi (SARS) a cikin 2003; don haka Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke haifar da ita ana kiranta CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa duk ƙasar da kuma wasu ƙasashe kusan 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da sabbin mutane sama da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da warkewar sama da 40,000 da mutuwar sama da 3,000.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "Maƙiyi na 1" kuma yana iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 game da COVID-19 wanda ya haɗa da bayanai game da kwayar cutar, cututtuka, abubuwan da ke haifar da su, bincike da magani tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya gano tsarin kwayar cutar da aka ware daga marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan binciken yana da nufin gabatar da binciken da aka yi a wannan sabon filin wasa wanda ke ci gaba da sauri.
Da farko, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da wata cuta da ke haifar da CoV, ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya ɓarke a cikin 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da yadda za mu guji kamuwa da cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa ba.
CoVs an ɗauka cewa ƙwayoyin cuta ne masu ƙarancin haɗari ga mutane, suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na kamuwa da cutar mura 4.
A wannan karni, mun sami CoVs guda biyu masu haɗari ga ɗan adam, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da kamuwa da cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da cutar da kashe mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine CoV na uku da aka sani a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto.Hoto.1,1, an fara bayar da rahoton cutar tarin fuka a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an fitar da tsarin CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, an samu rahoton mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar daga Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, cutar ta yadu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwan da ke kewaye, da ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an sanar da likitocin cutar, wanda ke nufin cewa mutane na iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar watsawa daga mutane.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da duk zirga-zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti game da cutar ya nuna cewa, daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka isa kasuwar kifin Wuhan kai tsaye inda ake tsammanin cutar ta samo asali ne daga wata dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin da aka wallafa wannan rahoton, cutar ta yadu zuwa China da ƙasashe kusan 50 a duniya (Hotuna (Hotuna.2).2).
Yayin da yanayi ya canja, ba a san yadda matsalar za ta kasance ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken da aka yi a wurare daban-daban na mutane 8,866 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 4,021 ya ba da sabon ma'anar cutar (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yana kamuwa da mutane a kowane zamani, amma sama da shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na masu cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan sun kasance ƙasa da 20, kuma kawai 14 daga cikin masu cutar sun kasance ƙasa da shekaru 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance a cikin maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya fi yawaita a cikin mutane fiye da Hubei da kewayenta.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga lokacin da ya fara zuwa lokacin da aka gano shi.
Aƙalla kwanaki 4.8 ne alamun cutar suka soma bayyana.
Lokaci daga lokacin da aka gano shi zuwa lokacin da ya mutu ya kai kwanaki 9.5 (4.8-13).
Yawan masu haihuwa, R0 ya kasance 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), yayin da ƙimar R0 da aka gyara ta kasance 2.23-4.82.
Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ya karu kafin ranar 23 ga Janairu, 2020, saboda yawan mutanen da suka yi tafiya kafin bikin bazara na kasar Sin.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya ya kasance 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), yayin da yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya ya kasance 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku masu mahimmanci na COVID-19 sune jima'i (maza), shekaru (≥60), da cutar nimoniya mai tsanani.
