Ta hanyar amfani da na'urorin bincike, an gano ƙwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin hanyoyin numfashi.
An gano enzymes ACE2 a cikin SARS-CoV-2 da kuma SARS-CoV.
A gefe guda, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da enzymes na ACE2 amma ba shi da ƙarfi kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da ƙananan haɗari ga mutane idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana iya samar da wani ɗan gajeren furotin da ba a taɓa gani ba wanda ake kira orf3b da furotin mai ɓoyewa wanda ake kira orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 orf3b na iya zama mai cutarwa ga mutane kuma yana hana IFNβ bayyana; duk da haka, orf8 ba shi da wani abu mai aiki.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, da abokan aiki, sun nuna cikakken tsarin cryo-EM na enzyme ACE2 a ƙuduri na 2.9 Å a cikin amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa wannan mahaɗin, wanda ya ƙunshi atom guda biyu, an tsara shi a matsayin kwayar halitta ta atom kuma cewa mahaɗin ACE2-B0AT1 na iya haɗa sunadarai na S, yana ba da tabbacin gano CoV da mai kamuwa da cutar.
B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin magani don gwajin maganin rigakafin SARS-CoV-2.
Tushen da ya sa aka yi wannan
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV duka sun samo asali ne daga bera kuma sun bazu zuwa mutane ta hanyar ƙuda da raƙumi, a cikin wannan kwayar.
Idan aka kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran CoVs, ana ɗaukar kwari a matsayin mafi kyawun hanyar watsa SARS-CoV-2 saboda yana da kusan 96% kama da wasu CoVs masu kama da SARS guda biyu waɗanda aka gano a cikin kwari, bat-SL-CoVZX45 da bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Amma, ba a san ainihin dabbar da ta sa ta tsallake wannan shingen zuwa wurin mutane ba, kuma ba a san hanyar da ta bi ba.
Ji, da abokan aikinsa sun yi tunanin cewa macizai sun canja kwayar cutar daga kura zuwa mutane ta hanyar musayar kwayoyin S protein.
A cewar wani bincike, masu bincike a Guangzhou, China, sun nuna cewa pangolin - dabba mai cin kwari da ake amfani da ita a cikin maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin - na iya zama mai ɗaukar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa mutane bisa ga kamanceceniya ta kwayoyin halitta 99% na CoV da aka gano a cikin harshe da SARS-CoV-2.
Amma, bambancin kashi 1 cikin 100 tsakanin kwayoyin halitta biyu yana da girma sosai; saboda haka, ba a sami cikakkiyar shaida ba tukuna (Fig. 33).
Ba a san yawancin kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 ba tukuna.
Kwayoyin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV na iya rayuwa a cikin gilashi har tsawon awanni 48 a cikin yanayin bushewa da kwanaki 5 a cikin zafin jiki 20 °C da 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samun wasu halaye.
An nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 ba ya kamuwa da hasken rana (ultraviolet rays) da zafin jiki na 56 °C na tsawon minti 30; a cikin kashi 75%, chlorine, peracetic acid, calcium, da sauran magungunan ƙwayoyin cuta, amma ba chlorhexidine ba, suna kashe kwayar cutar sosai.
Yawancin mutane ba su da rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka suna iya kamuwa da cutar.
A halin yanzu, babu wani bincike da aka yi game da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
