A wani ɓangare kuma, ƙwayar cuta tana sa a samu ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa da ke sa huhu da sauran gabobin jiki su lalace, wasu kuma suna sa gabobin jiki su kasa aiki kuma wasu kuma su mutu.
Kwayar SARS-CoV-2, wanda aka gano a cikin mutane na farko, tana da alama tana shafar tsofaffi da ke da wasu cututtuka da mata masu ciki.
A yawancin lokaci, mutanen da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta ko kuma waɗanda ba su da ƙwayoyin cuta suna da saurin kamuwa da cuta fiye da wasu.
Lokacin bayyanar cututtuka na SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance daga kwanaki 1-14, yawanci kwanaki 3-7 bisa ga binciken da aka yi akan marasa lafiya 425 na farko a Wuhan.
Amma, binciken da aka yi kan marasa lafiya 1,099 ya nuna cewa a matsakaita, alamun cutar suna faruwa ne bayan kwana 3 kuma daga 0 zuwa 24.
Wani bincike da aka yi kwanan nan, wanda aka ambata ɗazu, ya nuna cewa yawan ciwon yana da kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) bisa ga mutane 8,866.
Yana da mahimmanci ga ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya su sanya ranakun keɓewa dangane da lokacin da cutar ke nuna alamun cutar, don hana mutane masu cutar amma ba su da alamun cutar cutar.
A al'adance, mutanen da ke cikin yanayin cutar ko kuma waɗanda ke da cutar suna bukatar su keɓe kansu na kwanaki 14.
Shin ya kamata a kara wa mutane kwanaki 24 a keɓe su?
Zazzabin zazzabi shine mafi yawan alamun farko na COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa ba tare da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ba kamar bushewar hanci, wahalar numfashi, ciwon tsoka, zazzabi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, hanci, ciwon kirji, gudu, numfashi mai sauƙi, da hanci.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami wahalar numfashi da / ko rashin iskar oxygen a cikin mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
A cikin yanayi mafi tsanani, marasa lafiya suna da saurin kamuwa da rashin ruwa a cikin huhu, rashin jini (septic shock), acidosis na metabolism, da coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabin cizon sauro da/ko alamun da ke tattare da zazzabin zazzabin zazzabin sauro, koda kuwa ba su da wata cuta a cikin huhu, ya kamata a fara bincikar su don gano ko suna da cutar.
Binciken marasa lafiya na Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98% na alamun cutar sun kasance a kan kumburi, kashi 76% a kan tari mai bushe, kashi 55% a kan wahalar numfashi, da kashi 3% a kan gudu; kashi 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar kayan aikin numfashi.
An gano irin wannan binciken a cikin bincike biyu da aka yi a kan marasa lafiya na iyali ɗaya da marasa lafiya da ba su da alamun cutar.
A kwatankwacin haka, binciken ɗan adam na 2012 ya nuna cewa masu cutar MERS-CoV suna da zazzabin cizon sauro (98%), tari mai zafi (47%), da wahalar numfashi (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun su.
Amma, kashi 80% na su sun buƙaci taimakon numfashi, musamman marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma wannan ya zo ne saboda gaskiyar cewa MERS ya fi COVID-19 haɗari.
An kuma lura da zubar da jini (26%) da kuma ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiyar SARS, an nuna zazzabin cizon sauro (99%-100%), bushewar hanci (29%-75%), wahalar numfashi (40%-42%), gudu (20-25%), ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) sune manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka kuma ana buƙatar kayan aikin numfashi a cikin 14%-20% na marasa lafiya.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, yawan mutuwar COVID-19 ya kai kashi 2% yayin da aka tabbatar da cutar a duniya a cikin mutane 66,576.
A wani ɓangare kuma, mutuwar SARS a watan Nuwamba 2002 ya kai kashi 10 cikin ɗari na mutane 8,096 da aka yi wa gwaji.
A cikin MERS, yawan mutanen da suka mutu a watan Yuni na shekara ta 2012 ya kai kashi 37 cikin ɗari na mutane 2,494 da aka gano.
Binciken da aka yi a baya ya nuna cewa R0 na SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance mafi girma a 6.47 yayin da CI ya kasance kashi 95% a cikin 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya kasance tsakanin 2 zuwa 4.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da MERS-CoV da SARA-CoV dangane da alamun cututtuka, yanayin cutar, da R0 an nuna su a cikin Tebur na 1.1.
Waɗannan ƙididdigar sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da ƙwarewar watsawa fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma ba kamar sauran biyun ba.
Saboda haka, yana da wuya a rage cutar SARS-CoV-2 fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Mutane da yawa da ke da cutar za su zauna a gida ɗaya ko kuma a cikin mota ɗaya.
Masu cutar sun yi tafiya daga ko sun zauna a Wuhan ko wasu wuraren da cutar ta bulla ko kuma sun kasance tare da mutanen da ke da cutar ko kuma waɗanda ke da cutar a cikin makonni biyu kafin cutar.
Koyaya, an ba da rahoton cewa mutane na iya kamuwa da cutar ba tare da nuna alamun cutar ba sama da makonni biyu kuma marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma aka sallame su daga asibiti na iya sake kamuwa da cutar, wanda ke nuna buƙatar ƙara lokacin keɓewa.
Marasa lafiya suna da ƙarancin ƙwayoyin farin jini (musamman ƙwayoyin lymphocytes) a farkon lokacin.
Misali, an gano cutar lymphopenia da ƙididdigar farin jini &lt; 4×109/L gami da ƙididdigar lymphocyte &lt; 1×109/L, tare da haɓaka aspartate aminotransferase da viremia a cikin marasa lafiya 1,099 na COVID-19.
An ƙara yawan enzymes na hanta da myoglobin a cikin jinin wasu marasa lafiya, kuma sun sami haɓakar furotin mai aiki da C da kuma erythrocyte a cikin mafi yawan marasa lafiya.
A cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani, yawan D-dimer, wanda shine samfurin lalacewar fibrin a cikin jini, ya karu, kuma yawan lymphocytes ya ragu.
Yawancin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 suna da ciwon kirji wanda ke tattare da ciwon huhu (duhu mai launi biyu ko rashin haske na gilashin ƙasa).
Marasa lafiya suna fama da ciwon huhu, cutar huhu, da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (acute respiratory distress syndrome, ARDS).
A lokacin ARDS, akwai ciwon jini da kuma ruwa mai yawa, kuma nama yana rufe raunuka wanda ke haifar da matsalolin samun iska.
Pneumocytes na nau'in I da na II (nau'in-I da nau'in-II pneumocytes) suna rage yawan abubuwan da ke cikin farfajiya kuma suna ƙara matsa lamba a cikin iska, wanda ke rage ƙarfin numfashi don faɗaɗa kuma yana ƙara damar numfashi don kasawa.
Saboda haka, sakamakon gwajin nono mafi muni sau da yawa yana nuna yanayin cutar mafi muni.
