Shin kwayar cutar tana shafar kwayar cutar ACE2 a wasu sassan jiki?
Idan ba mu da amsoshi masu kyau ga waɗannan tambayoyin, ba za mu iya bincika cutar da sauri ba kuma ba za mu iya samun magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe ne za a daina wannan ciwon?
Ta yaya kwayoyin halitta suke canjawa yayin da suke yaduwa?
Shin zai zama matsalar duniya, zai ƙare kamar SARS ko zai sake dawowa a matsayin mura?
Yana da muhimmanci mu bincika amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa.
