Kwayar cutar corona ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi
Juyin halittar kwayoyin halitta ya haifar da canjin kwayoyin coronaviruses (CoVs) da kuma na dabbobi, gami da mutane, a cikin dubunnan shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayoyin cutar CoVs na mutum (HCoVs) suna haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da cuta, kamar mura.
Fashewar cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) da cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun canza yanayin kuma sun nuna yadda cutar HCoV ke da haɗari da kisa.
Barkewar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake dawo da CoVs a cikin ɗakin ajiya kuma ya ba mu mamaki yadda yake saurin yaduwa da rashin lafiya idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV.
HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi kuma fahimtar asalin HCoVs na dabbobi yana da amfani sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs suna fitowa ne daga ƙwari kuma ba sa cutarwa.
An kuma gano wasu dabbobin da HCoVs ke fara kamuwa da su kafin su shiga cikin mutane.
Sanin dabbobin da ke kamuwa da cutar yana da amfani wajen hana cutar.
Binciken alaƙar da ke tsakanin dabbobi da ke dauke da CoV na iya taimakawa wajen gano cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, mun taƙaita abubuwan da aka gano kwanan nan game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin su a cikin dabbobi da kuma yadda suka bazu tsakanin dabbobi daban-daban.
Mafi mahimmanci, mun gano kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance tsakanin HCoVs daban-daban ta hanyar nazarin juyin halitta na kwayar cuta da sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
Ana magana ne game da cutar CoV 2019 (COVID-19) a halin yanzu.
An kuma tattauna yadda kwayoyin halitta da ke dauke da cutar ke canzawa da kuma yadda cutar ke sa mutane su kamu da cutar.
Kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) ta kasance cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ke da tarin ƙwayoyin cuta masu ɗauke da ƙwayoyin cuta, kowannensu yana da ƙwayoyin cuta masu ɗauke da ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma suna da RNA guda ɗaya.
Wannan kwayar cuta tare da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta na 26 na 32 kilobases a cikin RNA an kira shi CoVs saboda siffar kambi da aka gani a cikin yisti.
A cikin tsari, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta da ba a rarraba su ba kuma suna tare.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da manyan filayen biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), wanda ke haifar da pp1a da pp1ab polyproteins.
Bayan haka, sai a haɗa su zuwa sunaye 16 da ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta yana da ORFs a kan sunadarai masu gina jiki, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Ana kuma sanya sunadarai masu yawa na asali a cikin layin CoV.
Dangane da bambance-bambance a cikin tsarin furotin, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa manyan rukuni huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), wanda beta-CoV shine mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa layi huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Sakamakon bincike ya nuna cewa kwari da sauro sune tushen alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune tushen gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi kuma wasu sun zama tushen cutar ɗan adam.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an gano mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoV.
A cikin waɗannan HCoVs HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune nau'in alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun haɗa da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus mai ciwo mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), coronavirus mai ciwon numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 suna haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar mura da / ko tari.
Akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 suna da cutarwa sosai, suna shafar ƙananan ƙwayar cuta a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya kuma suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtuka na waje.
An gano asalin HCoV-229E, B814, a cikin hanjin marasa lafiya na mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin bincike ta hanyar bincike mai zurfi game da HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu suna haifar da alamun cutar kai tsaye.
A zahiri, an yarda da shi cewa kamuwa da HCoVs gabaɗaya ba shi da haɗari har zuwa barkewar SARS.
Cutar SARS ta barke a shekara ta 2003 kuma ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin bala'i mafi muni a tarihin kwanan nan, tare da kamuwa da mutane fiye da 8,000 da kashi 10% na mutuwar da ake tsammani.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar murhun numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta haifar da annoba a yankin Gulf da ke yaduwa zuwa sauran sassan duniya.
