Akwai yiwuwar cewa CoVs da ke yada cututtuka daga dabbobi zuwa mutane ba su haɗu ba saboda fitowar sabon CoV mai saurin yaduwa da / ko daga mutane.
Dole ne a dakatar da cin namun daji a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin don rage hulɗar da ba dole ba tsakanin mutane da dabbobi.
A yayin da muke fuskantar cutar SARS, MERS da COVID-19, ya kamata a sami shirye-shirye da shirye-shiryen magance su.
Hakika, ƙwayoyin cuta sun daɗe suna rayuwa a duniya.
Suna zama a inda suke har sai sun sami zarafi su ƙaura.
Ko da yake ƙudaje suna da ayyuka masu yawa da suke sa su iya yaɗa ƙwayoyin cuta, za a iya rage haɗarin haɗuwa da ƙudaje da sauran dabbobi idan aka gaya wa mutane su guji kusantarsu.
Ana buƙatar ci gaba da bincike a cikin kwayoyin halittar mutum don ƙarin fahimtar yanayin CoVs da kuma yanayin halittu na halitta wanda zai zama da amfani wajen hana yaduwar cututtuka daga dabba zuwa mutum da kuma cutar a nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi kyau ta hana ƙwayoyin cuta daga dabbobi zuwa mutane ita ce ta hana mutane daga wuraren da ƙwayoyin cuta ke watsawa daga dabbobi zuwa mutane.
Har yanzu ba a san asalin SARS-CoV-2 ba daga dabbobi zuwa mutane.
Da farko, idan kwari suna yada kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin pangolin, yana da kyau a bincika yanayin da kwari da pangolin ke raba su a cikin yanayin su.
Na biyu, idan ƙwari na taka rawa wajen yada cututtuka kai tsaye tsakanin mutane, to, ya kamata a yi la'akari da yadda mutane ke hulɗa da ƙwari.
Na uku, idan an ga cewa dabba mai kama da mutum tana aiki ne a matsayin mai kula da ƙwayoyin cuta, to, ya kamata a bayyana yadda ya bambanta da sauran halittu, ciki har da mutane, bats da pangolins.
A ƙarshe, saboda yawancin dabbobin gida da suka haɗa da dabbobin gida suna iya kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, ana buƙatar yin bincike da gwaji don cutar.
Idan kwari ne, pangolin ko wani dabba mai kama da mutum, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu kama da juna za a gano su a cikin yanayin da ke tattare da cutar.
Ƙarin bincike a kan wannan batun zai bayyana yanayin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, gami da sakamako mai mahimmanci a cikin rigakafin COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar daidaita tushen tabbatar da mai haƙuri wanda ake zargi da wanda aka tabbatar  don samun COVID-19
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta fitar da jagororin gaggawa don ganowa da kuma kula da mutanen da ke da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda ke nuna ƙwarewarmu da kuma yadda za mu magance cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, wanda iliminmu game da ita yana ƙaruwa bisa ga binciken da ake ci gaba da yi da kuma hanyoyin da ake kira magani; saboda haka, bincike da hanyoyin magani suna ci gaba da canzawa.
A cikin wannan wasikar, mun amsa tambaya guda game da manufofinmu kuma mun ba da sababbin ka'idoji don yanke shawara ƙididdigar  da  tabbatarwa  bisa ga sababbin ka'idoji na Ganowa da Kula da COVID-19 (fassarar ta bakwai)) da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiyar Jama'ar Sin ya bayar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus na 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da cutar, yanzu ana kiranta da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sake ta da cutar ta coronavirus mai saurin numfashi 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga watan Agusta 2020, WHO ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin matsalar kiwon lafiya ta duniya.
Don magance SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka takaddun gaggawa waɗanda aka buga akan layi a cikin Binciken Likita na Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
An yi amfani da su sosai tun lokacin da aka wallafa su.
Ya kamata a lura cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, kuma iliminmu game da ita yana ƙaruwa bisa ga binciken da ake ci gaba da yi da kuma hanyoyin da ake bi don magance ta; saboda haka, ana iya daidaita bincike da hanyoyin magani.
Sakamakon Bincike da Kula da COVID-19 wanda Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya gudanar tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Agusta, 2020, ya fitar da rahotanni bakwai na wasu lokuta masu tsanani.
Zhou da abokan aikinsa sun ba da shawarar tsarin bincike mai sauƙi bisa ga binciken asibiti.
Aikin da suka yi ya ƙarfafa bangaskiyarmu kuma ya sa muka san cewa wannan matsalar ta shafi dukan duniya.
Muna yaba musu don aikinsu mai kyau.
Koyaya, aikin su yana buƙatar sabuntawa dangane da sababbin Ka'idojin Ganowa da Kula da COVID-19 (Sakamakon 7th) da sababbin bincike.
A cewar fitowar ta bakwai (3 ga Maris 2020), tabbatar da mai haƙuri mai haƙuri yana buƙatar haɗuwa da ɗaya daga cikin ƙa'idodin tarihin asibiti da ƙididdigar asibiti guda biyu don yanke shawara, ko kuma yana buƙatar cika ƙa'idodin asibiti guda uku idan babu tarihin asibiti mai kyau:
Tarihin kamuwa da cutar: (1) ya kasance a cikin Wuhan da kewayenta, ko kuma ya kasance a cikin wani yanki da aka gano wani mai cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar alamun cutar; (2) ya kasance a cikin kusanci da mutane masu cutar SARS-CoV-2 (a cikin gwajin kwayar nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) ya kasance a cikin kusanci da masu fama da zazzabin cizon sauro ko masu fama da cutar ta COVID-19 daga Wuhan da kewayenta, ko kuma wasu yankuna da aka gano cutar a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar alamun cutar; (4) ya kasance a cikin kusanci da masu cutar da aka tabbatar (ƙananan marasa lafiya 2 da zazzabi da / ko a cikin makonni 2 a cikin wuraren da ba a san su ba, kamar gida, makaranta, ƙungiyoyi, ko cibiyoyi).
Alamun asibiti: (1) zazzabi da / ko wahalar numfashi; (2) alamun cutar COVID-19; (3) ƙarancin ƙwayoyin jini na farko ko ƙarancin ƙwayoyin lymphocyte.
Tabbatar da cutar ya kamata a yi shi ne a kan mai haƙuri mai cutar ko kuma gwajin ruwan jiki kamar yadda aka nuna a ƙasa: (1) lokacin da gwajin PCR na yau da kullun ya nuna tabbataccen cutar SARS-CoV-2; (2) lokacin da jerin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar suka nuna kamanceceniya da sabon coronavirus; (3) lokacin da gwajin ruwan jikin ya nuna cewa mutum yana da maganin IgM da IgG na kansa da ke hana SARS-CoV-2; ko kuma canjin maganin antibody na SARS-CoV-2 daga mara kyau zuwa tabbatacce, ko kuma titer ya tashi sau ≥4 a lokacin murmurewa fiye da na lokacin cutar.
Mun lura cewa an ƙara gwajin PCR na atomatik don gano nucleic acid a cikin jini ko jini a cikin fitowar ta biyu (18 ga Janairu 2020) da ta uku (22 ga Janairu 2020).
An ƙara binciken jini a fitowar ta huɗu (27 ga Janairu 2020) da ta biyar (8 ga Fabrairu 2020); kuma an ƙara tabbacin gwajin ruwa a fitowar ta bakwai.
Wannan canjin ya dogara ne akan ƙoƙarin masu bincike don gano wani abu wanda zai iya tabbatar da ingancin nucleic acid don saurin gwaji, da kuma samfurin daga tarin jini, wanda ya kara yawan gwajin da ake samu, kuma ya ba da damar samun kwayoyin cutar da kansu a matsayin tushen tabbatar da cutar.
Ƙari ga haka, akwai ƙarin tabbaci da ke tuna mana mu mai da hankali ga marasa lafiya da ba su da alamun cutar.
Don haka, allon Zhou da abokan aikinsa ya cancanci sake fasalin, saboda ya nuna mutumin da ba shi da alamun cutar a matsayin  low risk.
Wannan tsarin gwajin (tsarin ƙimar) yana buƙatar tabbatarwa a wasu asibitoci da kuma wasu bincike.
A taƙaice, muna fatan cewa za a sami ƙarin tabbaci kuma muna gayyatar masu karatu su yi magana game da su.
Da sanin abin da aka yi hasashensa kuma aka tabbatar da shi, mun yanke shawarar yadda za mu bi da kuma bi da dokokin da aka kafa na al'ummanku.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta sabunta abubuwan da muke bi don taimaka muku.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton wasu mutane biyar da suka mutu daga COVID-19, mafi yawan mutuwar yau da kullun
Jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da cewa wasu mutane biyar sun mutu daga COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadin mafi girma a cikin rana guda da cutar ta kashe.
A jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta yi rajistar mutane 114 da suka warke kuma 33 a gida.
Mutane 17 ne suka mutu.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar a shafin yanar gizo, jami'in IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ya ce wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr Meerjady, biyu daga cikin wadanda suka mutu sun haura shekaru 60, biyu suna tsakanin shekaru 51 zuwa 60, ɗayan kuma yana tsakanin shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
Ya kuma ce biyu daga cikin mutanen daga Dhaka ne.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya shaida wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Anadolu Agency cewa, daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, jami'in hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengal, wanda ake kula da shi a asibitin Kuwait Maitree.
A ranar Asabar, Ministan Sufuri na Bangladesh Obaidul Quader ya sanar a cikin wani sanarwar bidiyo cewa za a dakatar da duk zirga-zirgar jiragen sama na tsawon lokaci fiye da yadda aka tsara, har zuwa Asabar mai zuwa.
An fara dakatar da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a ranar 26 ga Maris kuma an shirya za a kawo karshen a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
Ana ba da izinin sufuri na kayayyaki masu muhimmanci - magani, mai da abinci.
An gano mutane biyu da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a Bangladesh a ranar 8 ga watan Maris, wadanda suka dawo daga Italiya da matar daya daga cikin mutanen.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, dukan ukun sun warke.
SARS-CoV-2 ya yi sanadiyar kamuwa da mutane miliyan daya a duniya
A ranar Alhamis, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta SARS-CoV-2 ya zarce miliyan daya a duk duniya kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin wani rahoto daga Jami'ar Johns Hopkins.
Akalla mutane dubu 52 aka ce sun mutu sakamakon COVID-19, cutar da ke haifar da coronavirus.
An cimma wannan a ranar da Malawi ta tabbatar da cutar ta farko kuma a lokaci guda Zambia ta sami mutuwar mutum daya daga coronavirus.
A ranar Alhamis, Koriya ta Arewa ta ce tana cikin ƙasashen da ba su da cutar coronavirus.
A ranar Laraba ne Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da rahoton sabbin kamuwa da cutar 1,051,635 da suka hada da kamuwa da cutar 79,332 a cikin sa'o'i 24 da suka gabata da karfe 4 na safe, a lokacin Turai ta Tsakiya (0800 UTC) a ranar 4 ga Afrilu.
A Amirka, an samu mutane fiye da 244,000 da suka kamu da cutar kuma aƙalla 5,900 sun mutu.
CBS News ta ambaci Jami'ar Johns Hopkins da cewa, a Amurka akwai mutane sama da 1,000 da suka mutu a ranar Laraba sakamakon cutar coronavirus.
A dukan duniya, ƙasashe sun yi shelar cewa za a ɗauki matakai don hana yaduwar cututtuka.
A ranar Alhamis, magajin garin Moscow Sergei Sobyanin, ya tsawaita dokar hana fita ta birnin har zuwa ranar 1 ga Mayu.
A duk fadin kasar, Shugaba Vladimir Putin ya sanar da cewa za a biya 'yan Rasha duk da cewa ba za su dawo bakin aiki ba har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
Majalisar dokokin Portugal ta kada kuri'ar kara wa'adin kwanaki 15 na zaman majalisar; mafi yawan mutane 215 sun goyi bayanta, 10 sun ki amincewa da shi kuma daya bai goyi bayansa ba.
Saudiyya ta tsawaita lokacin shan kofi a biranen alfarma na Makka da Madina zuwa rana ɗaya; a baya, ana shan kofi daga karfe 9 na yamma zuwa 12 na safe.
Thailand ta shirya kofi tsakanin karfe 4 na dare da karfe 10 na dare.
Gwamnan Ohio, Mike DeWine, ya sanar da cewa jihar ta tsawaita dokar hana fita har zuwa ranar 1 ga Mayu.
Kasuwancin Australiya suna da iyaka kan yawan kayan da mutum zai iya saya a lokaci ɗaya
A ranar Lahadi da Asabar da yamma, manyan kantunan sayar da kayayyaki na Woolworths da Coles na Australiya da ke fadin kasar suna sanya iyakar sayen kayan kwalliya a kan mutum ya sayi guda biyu ko kuma kowanne daga cikin shagunan biyu.
ALDI kuma ta kafa iyaka ga wata 'yar'uwa a ranar Litinin.
An nuna wannan haramcin a matsayin saƙo ga jama'a a kan shafukan Facebook na kamfanonin.
An umarci masu sayayya da su kasance cikin shiri saboda tsoron COVID-19 yayin da mutane ke buƙatar keɓewa.
A ranar Laraba, Woolworths ta rage yawan kayan da ake sayarwa da kuma aikawa gida a matsayin guda a rana.
Waɗannan canje-canjen sun biyo bayan ƙuntatawa na farko na farashin kaya na farko da Woolworths da Coles suka gabatar a ranar 4 da 5 ga Maris a cikin kamfanonin biyu a cikin jerin.
A cikin wasiƙar Coles ta 8 ga Maris, ya bayyana cewa an dakatar da haramcin, "shaguna da yawa sun ƙare a cikin awa ɗaya bayan kawo su", kuma ya ce bukatar ba ta taɓa faruwa ba, yayin da ALDI, wanda ya rubuta a Facebook a ranar Talata ya ce "ba zato ba tsammani".
Sayarwa ta "yi tashin gwauron zabi" a makon da ya gabata a cewar wani mai magana da yawun Woolworths.
Wani babban kanti na Costco a Canberra ya kuma sanya iyaka kan farashin da aka yarda da shi a kan wasu kayan kwalliya biyu a makon da ya gabata.
Don rage ƙarancin, Coles ya ba da ƙarin aiki kuma ya ƙara yawan aiki, Woolworths ya ba da ƙarin aiki, kuma ALDI ta kawo ƙarin kamar yadda aka shirya a ranar Laraba ta musamman.
Russell Zimmerman, shugaban kungiyar masu sayar da kayayyaki ta Australiya, ya ce masu sayar da kayayyaki suna kokarin kara yawan kayayyakin da suke sayar da su amma takunkumin da hukumomi suka sanya kan yawan motocin da ke kawo su ya kawo matsala.
Yana sa ran samun ƙarin kuɗi, yayin da ma'aikata suke ƙoƙarin biyan bukatun da ake da su kuma suna da kwanakin hutu kaɗan.
A ranar Talata, ALDI ta sanar da cewa bayan fitar da kayan da aka saita don sayarwa da sauri, wasu shagunan ba za su iya yin wani abu daban ba a ranar Laraba.
A wani rahoto da News.com.au ta bayar, Dokta Gary Mortimer, masanin sayar da kayan gargajiya daga Jami'ar Fasaha ta Queensland, ya ce kasuwanni suna kawo sayarwa a kowane dare.
Ya ce, ƙwai suna da girma sosai, kuma hakan yana sa a rage yawan kayayyakin da ake sayarwa, har sa'ad da aka sayar da su, sai su zama da yawa kuma su zama kamar sun ƙare.
Russell Zimmerman ya rubuta a ABC News cewa "Coles da Woolworths sun yi tunanin cewa idan aka samu kayayyaki da yawa, kamar su kayan wanki da kuma wanke hannu, za a iya rage yawan kayan da ake amfani da su".
Wani mai aikin kwalliya da ke kiwon tumaki ya ce a ranar Laraba, ba a sami kwalliya ba.
Kimberly-Clark, mai kera takarda, da Solaris Paper mai kera Sorbent, sun tabbatar da cewa suna aiki 24/7 don ci gaba da biyan bukatun, a cewar rahoton News.com.au.
Shafin yanar gizo na Domain.com, wanda ke sayar da ƙasa da ƙasa ya ba da rahoton cewa akwai masu siyarwa da ke ba da kayan kwalliya kyauta ga wanda ya ci hammer a Melbourne, tare da ƙananan tallace-tallace saboda masu siye sun sami hutu a ƙarshen mako mai tsawo wanda ya haɗa da Ranar Ma'aikata.
A cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Alhamis a NT News, wata jarida ta yau da kullum a Darwin, an nuna wani littafi mai layi takwas da za a cire don amfani da shi a matsayin kayan aiki.
Da farko, shagunan sun ƙi ƙuntatawa, a cewar rahoton ABC Australia a ranar 3 ga Maris inda suka ce ba su da niyyar ƙuntatawa.
Russell Zimmerman ya daɗa cewa kayayyaki da aka sayar a kasuwa sun haɗa da abin rufe fuska, kayan wanke hannu, abinci mai ƙanshi, sabulu da kuma man shanu.
Hakazalika, a waje da Ostiraliya, a ranar Lahadi da yamma an ga kantin sayar da kayan kwalliya na Ocado yana hana sayen kayan kwalliyar Andres ta hanyar sayen tsakanin 2 da 12 na 'yan uwa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar ta duniya
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19  cutar da kwayar cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ta haifar a matsayin bala'in duniya.
Duk da cewa kalmar "matsanancin duniya" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda wasu cututtukan ke da haɗari ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar cewa gwamnatoci su ɗauki mataki:
"Dukan ƙasashe za su iya canja yadda wannan matsalar ta duniya take yaduwa.
Idan ƙasashe suka yi hankali, bincika, bi da, rarrabewa, sa ido da kuma tattara mutane kan wannan batun", in ji Babban Jami'in WHO, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
"Muna matukar damuwa da yadda cutar ke yaduwa da kuma yadda take da hatsari da kuma rashin kulawa".
A cewar Dokta Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amurka (CDC), cutar "ba zato ba tsammani".
Ya ce, a cikin wata sanarwa da aka buga a CNN a watan Fabrairu, "sai dai wannan, babu wani kwayar cutar da ta shafi hanyar numfashi da aka gano tun lokacin da ta bulla har zuwa yanzu".
Ghebreyesus ya ba da irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar coronavirus a duniya ba".
Ya daɗa cewa: "Ba mu ga cewa matsalar ta shafi dukan duniya ba".
Sabuwar matakin matsalar ta duniya ya zo ne bayan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yanke shawarar a watan Janairu ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin babbar matsalar lafiyar jama'a ta duniya.
Shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka, Dr. Anthony Fauci, ya ce wannan fashewar "ba za ta yiwu ba".
A ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da ke fama da COVID-19 a duk duniya, daga cikinsu 4,600 sun mutu.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019/20 ta duniya cuta ce mai yaduwa ta cutar 2019 (COVID-19), wacce kwayar cutar ta kamu da cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cutar 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin matsalar rashin lafiyar jama'a a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, sannan a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya a ranar 11 ga Agusta, 2020.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu 2020, an bayar da rahoton kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 210 da yankuna kuma kusan mutane 97,000 sun mutu.
Mutane 364,000 ne suka tsira.
An kiyasta yawan mutuwar a kasar Sin ya kai kashi 4%, yayin da a duniya ya kai kashi 13.04% a Algeria da .08% a New Zealand.
Alamun da ake gani a fili su ne zazzabi, tari, da kuma numfashi.
Matsalolin cutar na iya haɗawa da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Lokaci daga kamuwa da cutar zuwa bayyanar cututtuka shine kimanin kwanaki biyar amma yana iya kasancewa daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani maganin rigakafi ko magani da aka sani don cutar.
Maganin farko yana magance alamun cutar da kuma taimakawa da ƙananan taimako. Shawarwarin da aka ba da shawarar don hana cutar sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki lokacin da kake bayyana, nisanta kanka daga wasu, saka idanu da kuma ware kanka idan kana da wata shakka game da cutar.
Hukumomi a duk faɗin duniya sun amsa ta hanyar sanya takunkumin tafiya, keɓewa, kafe, kiyaye aiki da rufe wasu wurare.
Wannan ya haifar da rashin daidaituwa a cikin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar duniya, yana haɓaka ko dakatar da wasanni, bukukuwan addini, siyasa da al'adu, da kuma haifar da ƙarancin kayayyaki da ke haifar da yawan cin kasuwa.
An rufe makarantu da jami'o'i a ƙasashe ko yankuna a ƙasashe 193, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 na ɗalibai a duniya.
Labaran karya game da cutar sun bazu a kan intanet kuma an sami wasu lokuta na ƙiyayya da nuna bambanci ga Sinawa, wasu mutanen da ke fitowa daga Gabas da kudu maso gabashin Asiya ko kuma masu launin fata daga yankunan da cutar ta fi yaduwa.
Saboda rufe hanyoyin sufuri da manyan masana'antu, an rage gurɓataccen yanayi da fitar da iskar carbon.
Ma'aikatar lafiya a Wuhan, China (babban birnin lardin Hubei) ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai wasu ƙananan mutane da ba a san su ba tun daga ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara binciken a farkon Janairu, 2020.
An gano masu cutar a cikin alaƙar abincin teku a Huanan (Kasuwancin Kasuwancin Abinci na teku) kuma ana tsammanin cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi zuwa mutane.
Kwayar cutar da ke haifar da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cuta ce da aka gano wacce take kama da coronaviruses na bat, pangolin coronaviruses, da SARS-CoV. An gano mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma ba a gano cewa yana da alaƙa da kasuwar kayan lambu ba.
Daga cikin marasa lafiya da aka fara bayar da rahoto a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku na su sun kamu da cutar.
A ranar 13 ga watan Agusta, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a bayyana shi ba daga jaridar South China Morning Post ya ba da rahoton cewa mai yiwuwa mutum 55 ne ya kamu da cutar a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019, daga lardin Hubei. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa yayin da sabbin cututtukan suka ragu a China amma suka karu da sauri a Italiya, Iran, da Koriya ta Kudu, yawan sabbin cututtukan da ke wajen China ya fi na farko a cikin kasar Sin.
Wataƙila ba a ba da cikakken adadin masu cutar ba musamman waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu rahotanni kaɗan na kamuwa da cutar a cikin matasa masu shekaru 19 zuwa ƙasa da kashi 2.4% na kamuwa da cutar a duniya.Babban mai ba da shawara kan kimiyya a Burtaniya, Patrick Vallance, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya na iya kamuwa da cutar kafin a gano cutar a cikin jama'a.
Cutar ta shafi yawan mutanen da aka gwada su don COVID-19, kuma gwajin ya nuna tabbatacce ga cutar bisa ga bayanan hukuma.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta sami kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawanta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa ba su gwada waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya ba, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain, da Switzerland.
Binciken da aka fitar a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya nuna cewa a kasar Sin, har zuwa ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, kusan kashi 86 cikin dari na marasa lafiya ba a yi musu allurar rigakafi ba, kuma kashi 79 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ba a yi musu allurar rigakafi ba ne ke yin allurar rigakafi.
