Wanke hannu yana zuwa tare da sauran ayyukan tsabtace jiki a matsayin wani ɓangare na aikin ruwa, tsaftacewa da tsabta (WASH).
Wanke hannu yana hana kamuwa da cutar sankarar bargo, wadda ke yaduwa ta hanyar taɓa mutum kai tsaye.
Ƙananan haɗari na wanke hannuwan hannu a kai a kai shine ƙarancin fata.
Wani bincike da aka yi a Denmark a shekara ta 2012 ya nuna cewa yawan wanke hannu yana sa mutum ya yi zazzabi da kuma fari.
Ana kuma ganin wanke hannu sau da yawa a matsayin alamar wani abu da ake kira obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD).
Akwai lokuta guda biyar na rana da wanke hannu da sabulu ke da mahimmanci don rage kamuwa da cututtukan da ke wucewa ta bakin: bayan amfani da bayan gida (numfashi, wankewa), bayan wanke jariri (canza takalmin wanka), kafin ciyar da jariri, kafin cin abinci da lokacin da za a shirya / bayan cin abinci ko taɓa nama ko kifi.
Wasu yanayi da ake bukatar wanke hannu sosai don hana yaduwar cuta sun haɗa da kafin ko bayan an taɓa ƙwaro ko ƙwaro; bayan an husu, tari, ko hancin mutum; bayan an taɓa ƙwaro ko dabba; da kuma bayan an taɓa shara.
A ƙasashe da yawa, wanke hannu da sabulu ba shi da muhimmanci.
Binciken wanke hannu a cikin kasashe 54 a shekarar 2015 ya gano cewa a matsakaita, kashi 38.7% na iyalai suna wanke hannayensu da sabulu.Binciken na 2014 ya nuna cewa Saudi Arabiya ta kasance mafi girma a wanke hannu da kashi 97 cikin dari; Amurka tana cikin matsakaici da kashi 77 cikin dari; kuma China tana da kashi 23 cikin dari.A halin yanzu akwai canje-canje da yawa a cikin halayyar jama'a don inganta al'adun wanke hannu da sabulu a lokacin bala'i.Wasu yara suna wanke hannayensu a cikin rukuni a lokacin makaranta a rana tare da yin amfani da hannu a cikin yara a cikin ci gaban duniya.
